"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/994642","Department for Exiting the European Union ","false","2018-10-30","<p>The Protocol on Gibraltar will form part of the Withdrawal Agreement between the United Kingdom and the European Union. The Agreement will be laid in the House under section 13(1) of the European Union (Withdrawal) Act 2018 once negotiations are concluded. We expect to make the Memoranda available in due course once negotiations on the overall agreement between the United Kingdom, the Government of Gibraltar and Spain are complete.</p><p> </p>","Worcester","Mr Robin Walker",,"2018-10-30T16:54:20.877Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/994642/answer","Biography information for Mr Robin Walker","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/994642/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/994642/answer",,,,,,,,"203","Exiting the European Union ","Exiting the European Union ","2018-10-25","Gibraltar","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Exiting the European Union, pursuant to the oral contribution of the Prime Minister of 22 October 2018, Official Report, column 46, if he will place in the Library a copy of the (a) protocol and (b) underlying memoranda relating to Gibraltar.","false","Biography information for Liz McInnes","Heywood and Middleton","Liz McInnes","183976"
